1. Dependencies and Installing
=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%

 - POSIX compliant (Linux / MacOSX)
 - Windows support can very easely be added - You just need to implement the alive threading. Please send your patches, I'll add them to the project.

 - make && ./main   (try sudo ./main if the connection to the SMK fails)



2. Key bindings / Options
=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=

 - None atm

Just edit the source when you want to change something



3. Bug reports
=%=%=%=%=%=%=%

Please send bug reports to:

zillode@zillode.be

If you make any changes to the source, please mail me the 'diff -u' of the file(s) changed, and also why were the changes needed.



